&lt;li&gt;Experience in report writing (English/German), presentation preparation, stakeholder analysis and social media.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to demonstrate excellent written research and analysis for business audiences; must be able to synthesize large amounts of intelligence across numerous sources in a timely but thoughtful manner.&lt;/li&gt;
