&lt;li&gt;Identify barriers to adoption and work with the AI Lab to address them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track recurring issues and feedback themes to inform training, documentation and product improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Give input into the overall AI adoption plan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as first-line support for AI tools, answering user queries and troubleshooting common issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide practical guidance on effective prompting and workflow integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
