&lt;li&gt;Provide input into decisions on tool rollout, retirement, and optimisation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current with developments across the generative AI landscape (e.g. ChatGPT, GPTs, Claude and related tools) and assess their relevance to the firm.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
