&lt;h3&gt;Client Contribution &amp;amp; Handling&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft press releases, Q&amp;amp;As and key message documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show an ongoing interest in and grasp of media and market intelligence, and share that with clients and teams appropriately&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage in-house AI tools and other resources to manage workload and keep deliverables on track, on time and of the highest quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to brainstorms and pitch preparation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Think on a strategic and tactical level about client issues and account development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver ideas, direction and content&amp;nbsp;to the account team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce high quality client account deliverables that showcase the expertise, thinking, judgement and research behind our recommendations and strategic advice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a strong working relationship with internal and external clients and earn their trust&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Contribution to the Firm&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and maintain strong client and internal relationships, ensuring high-quality deliverables and responsiveness across multiple time-sensitive engagements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draw insights and opportunities from your personal and professional networks and leverage that knowledge appropriately on behalf of the Firm and our clients&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in and contribute to training sessions where appropriate&amp;nbsp;and take advantage of the learning and engagement opportunities when available&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Teamwork and Collaborative Approach&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the “eyes and the ears” of the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share ideas, knowledge and recommendations with the wider team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Earn the respect of their peers/colleagues and treat people with respect&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Communication Skills – Engagement with Media and Other Audiences&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare detailed reporter backgrounders and curate media lists to enhance our clients&#39; media presence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and assess media and visibility opportunities that can elevate our clients&#39; profiles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
